#|
A construction based on flat domains in ACL2, as introduced in
flat.lisp, of a function Z that satisfies the equation,

           (equal (Z x)
	          (if (equal x 0)
	              0
	              (* (Z (- x 1))(Z (+ x 1)))).
|#
